OL,3,CBristol Airport to change rules for
OL,4,Celectronics and liquids in carry-on
OL,5,Cbags
OL,7,FPassengers will be allowed to keep
OL,8,Fphones, laptops, and liquids in their
OL,9,Fhand luggage at Bristol Airport after
OL,10,Fa multi-million-pound upgrade to its
OL,11,Fscanners.
OL,13,FTravellers will no longer have to
OL,14,Frestrict liquids and toiletries to
OL,15,F100ml bottles and electrical items can
OL,16,Fremain in bags.
OL,18,FThe changes are because of a
OL,19,F#11.5million investment in security
OL,20,Fscanners. They will come into effect
OL,21,Fat Bristol Airport on 14 June.
