OL,7,FWhat are the new regulations?
OL,9,FThe new security rules include:
OL,11,FChief operating officer at Bristol
OL,12,FAirport Graeme Gamble said: "We are
OL,13,Fdelighted all customers travelling
OL,14,Ffrom Bristol Airport will benefit from
OL,15,Fstate-of-the-art technology being
OL,16,Fintroduced at security.
