OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1717106480
OL,3,CBristol Airport to change rules for
OL,4,Celectronics and liquids in carry-on
OL,5,Cbags
OL,7,F"The new equipment will reduce
OL,8,Fcustomer stress and inconvenience as
OL,9,Fthe need for 100ml liquids to be
OL,10,Fplaced in clear, plastic bags and
OL,11,Fremoved from hand baggage will no
OL,12,Flonger be required.
OL,14,F"The new process delivers a much more
OL,15,Fcustomer-friendly security operation
OL,16,Fusing the latest technology and
OL,17,Fproviding enhanced screening, allowing
OL,18,Fcustomers to keep personal items in
OL,19,Ftheir hand luggage.
