OL,3,CBristol Airport to change rules for
OL,4,Celectronics and liquids in carry-on
OL,5,Cbags
OL,7,F"However, customers should be reminded
OL,8,Fthere are no immediate changes to the
OL,9,Frules governing what can be taken
OL,10,Fthrough security as a result of this
OL,11,Finitiative, and the current hand
OL,12,Fluggage restrictions remain in place
OL,13,Funtil 14 June 2024."
OL,15,FBristol Airport is investing over
OL,16,F#400million in customer enhancements
OL,17,Fover the next five years, including a
OL,18,Fnew public transport interchange,
OL,19,Fadditional multi-storey car park, new
OL,20,Fretail and catering areas and other
OL,21,Fcustomer improvements.
