OL,7,FMr Gamble said: "For customers who
OL,8,Fhave booked Fast Track security, from
OL,9,F14 June until 31 July we are upgrading
OL,10,Fthe Fast Track security channels.
OL,12,F"Bookings will be unaffected, and the
OL,13,FFast Track Security priority service
OL,14,Fwill operate through a dedicated lane
OL,15,Fin the Central Search area.
OL,17,F"Customers will easily be able to
OL,18,Fidentify the Fast Track lane through
OL,19,Fthe additional signage and the
OL,20,Fsecurity team will be on hand to
OL,21,Fassist.
